According to the [docs|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Content+by+Label+Macro], the contentbylabel macro should sort by modified date when the sort parameter is not specified.

This is not working correctly. The following wiki markup produces lists sorted in different ways, when they should be identical:
{code}
{noformat}{contentbylabel:spec|space=@all}{noformat}
{contentbylabel:spec|space=@all}

{noformat}{contentbylabel:spec|sort=modified|space=@all}{noformat}
{contentbylabel:spec|sort=modified|space=@all}
{code}


See this page as an example:

http://qa-eac.atlassian.com/confluence/display/BUGS/contentbylabel+macro+again...

