When a confluence instance contains many spaces (hundreds of spaces, but often as little as dozens of spaces cause problems), the dashboard quickly becomes hard to use because the list of spaces causes the page to load slowly and makes the entire page super long.

It would be ideal if the space listing supported pagination, so that users could still access all the spaces from the dashboard, but not all the spaces would be listed at one time.

